button__disabled.html:
<mk-button mk-disabled=""><style>
  #root {
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    user-select: none;
    -moz-user-select: none;
    -ms-user-select: none;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
    width: 100%;
  }

  :host {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  :host([disabled]),
  :host([disabled]:focus) {
    cursor: default;
  }

  :host(:hover),
  :host(:focus) {
    outline: none;
  }
</style>
<button id="root" aria-disabled="true" mk-action-1="" tabindex="-1" disabled="">
  <slot>Button</slot>
</button>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="base/test.css"></mk-button>
